# Batch Management Fix — Implementation Plan

## Root Causes Found

| # | Problem | Impact |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | `BatchSchema` requires [session](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/lib/auth.ts#142-153) field — but test/assignment uploads don't have it | Seeds fail silently |
| 2 | Only `{ name: 1 }` unique index — no `{ program, joiningYear, intakeMonth }` dedup guard | Can create orphaned duplicates |
| 3 | Old batch name format: `2025BTECH` — client wants `BTECH_2025_JAN` | Name collisions, confusing UI |
| 4 | No CRUD REST API for batches — only a server action | Can't call from client-side TestManager |
| 5 | `academic-options` API requires `admin` role — teachers can't fetch batches for test upload | Teacher upload dropdowns are empty |
| 6 | [populateBatches](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/actions/academic.ts#132-189) only seeds 2020-2040 for `active` programs — if no programs exist yet, seeds nothing | Empty dropdown |
| 7 | `User.batch` references [Batch](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/%28admin%29/admin/students/page.tsx#16-17) ObjectId, but no migration ensures existing students are linked | Students have no batch → no tests shown |

---

## Proposed Changes

### Component 1 — Schema

---

#### [MODIFY] [Academic.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Academic.ts)

- Make [session](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/lib/auth.ts#142-153) field **optional** on BatchSchema (programs exist independently of sessions)
- Add compound unique index `{ program: 1, joiningYear: 1, intakeMonth: 1 }` with `unique: true`
- Keep `{ name: 1 }` unique index
- Add `batchCode` field in new format: `PROGRAM_CODE_YEAR_MONTH` e.g. `CSE_2026_JAN`
- Update [IBatch](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Academic.ts#53-69) interface accordingly

---

### Component 2 — Seeding Action

---

#### [MODIFY] [academic.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/actions/academic.ts)

Update [populateBatches()](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/actions/academic.ts#132-189):
- Use new batch code format `{CODE}_{YEAR}_{MONTH}` as both `name` and `batchCode`
- Remove hard [session](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/lib/auth.ts#142-153) dependency — set to `null` if not available
- Seed current year + next year by default (simpler, predictable)
- Also offer a full historical seed (2020-2040) as a separate admin action
- Add `{ upsert: true }` with compound key as filter (not just name)
- Return proper count of created vs skipped

---

### Component 3 — Batch CRUD API

---

#### [NEW] `/api/admin/batches/route.ts`

- [GET](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/student/fees/route.ts#7-48) — list batches, filterable by `?programId=`, `?year=`, `?intakeMonth=`, `?active=true`; populate program
- [POST](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/student/attendance/self-mark/route.ts#8-69) — create single batch with dedup check
- Server also exposes batch list to teachers (role check: `['admin', 'teacher']`)

#### [NEW] `/api/admin/batches/seed/route.ts`

- [POST](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/student/attendance/self-mark/route.ts#8-69) — trigger full seed (2020-2040, all active programs, both intakes)
- Idempotent — uses `updateOne({ filter }, { $setOnInsert: {...} }, { upsert: true })`
- Returns `{ created, skipped }`

#### [MODIFY] [academic-options/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/academic-options/route.ts)

- Allow both `admin` and `teacher` roles (teachers need it for test upload dropdowns)
- Return batches in new format with `batchCode`, `intakeMonth`, `joiningYear`

#### [MODIFY] [public/batches/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/public/batches/route.ts)

- Return `batchCode` and `intakeMonth` for registration form display

---

### Component 4 — Test Module Integration

---

#### [MODIFY] [admin/tests/route.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/tests/route.ts)

- After upload, verify batchId is a valid ProTest-linked Batch ObjectId

#### [MODIFY] [TestManager.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/components/admin/TestManager.tsx)

- Fetch batches from `/api/admin/batches?active=true` (new endpoint, same role)
- Display batch as `CSE_2026_JAN (Computer Science Engineering)` in dropdown

---

### Component 5 — Admin Batch Dashboard

---

#### [MODIFY] [BatchManager.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/components/admin/BatchManager.tsx)

- Add "Seed Batches" button that calls `/api/admin/batches/seed`  
- Shows created/skipped count in toast
- Refresh list after seed

---

## Verification Plan

### Automated
- `tsc --noEmit`
- API calls to `GET /api/admin/batches` → should return seeded batches
- `POST /api/admin/batches/seed` → should correctly create+skip

### Manual
1. Admin clicks "Seed Batches" → batches for current year + next year appear in dropdown
2. Teacher opens test upload → batch dropdown is populated
3. Same (program + year + intakeMonth) created twice → 2nd is silently skipped (no duplicate error)
4. Student assigned to batch → sees only that batch's tests
